<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph base="SL30860" id="IAS20_40" principles="yes"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>40</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 20"/><data name="paranum" value="40"/></prolog><body outputclass="bold"><p id="IAS20_P0069">An entity adopting the Standard for the first time shall: </p><ol outputclass="static" base="SL136213" id="IAS20_L0006" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL136215" id="IAS20_P0070">comply with the disclosure requirements, where appropriate; and</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL136217" id="IAS20_P0071">either:</p> <ol outputclass="static" base="SL136218" id="IAS20_L0007" type="lower-roman"><li><li_value>(i)</li_value> <p base="SL136220" id="IAS20_P0072">adjust its financial statements for the change in accounting policy in accordance with <xref base="F16452625" href="../ias08/IAS08_TOC.dita#IAS08_TOC0001/IAS08_TOC0001_V1" id="IAS20_X0037">IAS 8</xref>;  or</p></li><li><li_value>(ii)</li_value> <p base="SL136222" id="IAS20_P0073">apply the accounting provisions of the Standard only to grants or portions of grants becoming receivable or repayable after the effective date of the Standard.</p></li></ol></li></ol></body></paragraph>